#22454
The Memorial Grounds~
Many trees reach high above you, carefully placed around the section
known as the memorial grounds.  A number of small paths interweave across
the area, winding between markers of varying types, in memory of some of the
most famous gallants in Avendarian history.  A few memorials in the form of
statues are found about the grounds, their silver surfaces glinting in the
light.  The first is of a noble looking human swordmaster, another depicts a
man holding a harp, and another is of a female ethron woman proffering a
rose to the heavens.  To the north of here rises a small hill, while to the
south the accessories of the dueling yard can be seen.  The trees grow more
dense to the east, making passage impossible, while directly to the west,
the shrine of the rose stands.  
~
